  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Cash flow generation continues to demonstrate high quality. Q3 2025 operating cash flow totaled $27,867,000,000, with free cash flow of $24,405,000,000 after capital expenditures of $3,462,000,000. The free cash flow margin of 25.95% underscores Apple's exceptional cash conversion capabilities, providing substantial flexibility for capital allocation including stock buybacks of $21,075,000,000 during the quarter.",
